# Tasting Set System Implementation

## Overview
Das Tasting Set System implementiert eine 1:1 Beziehung zwischen Wanderungen (Hikes) und Whisky-Tasting-Sets. Jede Wanderung hat automatisch ein inklusives Tasting Set.

## Key Implementation Details

### 1. Database Schema
Das SQL-Schema definiert die 1:1 Beziehung:
```sql
-- 1:1 relationship with hikes
CREATE TABLE public.tasting_sets (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    hike_id INTEGER UNIQUE REFERENCES public.hikes(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0.00, -- Always 0 since included
    is_included BOOLEAN DEFAULT TRUE, -- Always true
    -- ... other fields
);
```

**Wichtige Constraints:**
- `hike_id UNIQUE` - Garantiert 1:1 Beziehung
- `price DEFAULT 0.00` - Tasting Set ist immer inklusive
- `is_included DEFAULT TRUE` - Immer im Hike-Preis enthalten

### 2. Model Structure

#### WhiskySample Model
```dart
@freezed
sealed class WhiskySample with _$WhiskySample {
  const factory WhiskySample({
    required int id,
    required String name,
    required String distillery,
    required int age,
    required String region,
    @JsonKey(name: 'tasting_notes') required String tastingNotes,
    @JsonKey(name: 'image_url') required String imageUrl,
    required double abv,
    String? category,
    @JsonKey(name: 'sample_size_ml') @Default(5.0) double sampleSizeMl,
    @JsonKey(name: 'order_index') @Default(0) int orderIndex,
  }) = _WhiskySample;
}
```

#### TastingSet Model
```dart
@freezed
sealed class TastingSet with _$TastingSet {
  const factory TastingSet({
    required int id,
    @JsonKey(name: 'hike_id') required int hikeId,
    required String name,
    required String description,
    required List<WhiskySample> samples,
    @Default(0.0) double price, // Always 0 since included
    @JsonKey(name: 'is_included') @Default(true) bool isIncluded, // Always true
    // ... other fields
  }) = _TastingSet;
}
```

### 3. Business Logic Extensions

#### TastingSet Extensions
```dart
extension TastingSetExtensions on TastingSet {
  bool get isCurrentlyAvailable { /* date logic */ }
  int get sampleCount => samples.length;
  double get totalVolumeMl => samples.fold(0.0, (sum, sample) => sum + sample.sampleSizeMl);
  String get formattedPrice => 'Inklusive'; // Always "Inklusive"
  String get mainRegion { /* most common region logic */ }
  double get averageAge { /* average calculation */ }
  double get averageAbv { /* average calculation */ }
}
```

#### WhiskySample Extensions
```dart
extension WhiskySampleExtensions on WhiskySample {
  String get formattedAge => '$age Jahre';
  String get formattedAbv => '${abv.toStringAsFixed(1)}%';
  String get formattedSampleSize => '${sampleSizeMl.toStringAsFixed(0)}ml';
  bool get hasCategory => category != null && category!.isNotEmpty;
  String get displayName => '$name ($distillery)';
}
```

### 4. Repository Pattern

#### TastingSetRepository
```dart
class TastingSetRepository {
  // Core methods for 1:1 relationship
  Future<TastingSet?> getTastingSetForHike(int hikeId);
  
  // Company management methods
  Future<TastingSet> createTastingSet({required int hikeId, ...});
  Future<TastingSet> updateTastingSet({required int tastingSetId, ...});
  Future<void> deleteTastingSet(int tastingSetId);
  
  // Utility methods
  Future<List<TastingSet>> getAllTastingSets();
  Future<List<TastingSet>> searchTastingSets(String query);
  Future<List<TastingSet>> getTastingSetsByRegion(String region);
}
```

### 5. UI Implementation

#### ViewModel (TastingSetSelectionViewModel)
```dart
class TastingSetSelectionViewModel extends ChangeNotifier {
  final Hike hike;
  TastingSet? _tastingSet;
  
  // Load single tasting set for hike (1:1 relationship)
  Future<void> _loadTastingSet() async {
    _tastingSet = await _tastingSetRepository.getTastingSetForHike(hike.id);
  }
  
  // Business logic getters
  int get totalSampleCount => _tastingSet?.sampleCount ?? 0;
  double get totalVolumeMl => _tastingSet?.totalVolumeMl ?? 0.0;
  String get mainRegion => _tastingSet?.mainRegion ?? 'Unbekannt';
}
```

#### UI Components
- **TastingSetSelectionPage**: Hauptseite für Tasting Set Anzeige
- **TastingSetInfoCard**: Informationskarte für Tasting Set Details
- **Keine Auswahl-Logik**: Nur informative Darstellung

### 6. Integration Points

#### With Hike System
- Tasting Set wird automatisch mit Hike geladen
- Keine separate Auswahl oder Preisberechnung
- Checkout integriert Tasting Set automatisch

#### With Company System
- Unternehmen verwalten Tasting Sets für ihre Wanderungen
- RLS-Policies schützen Company-Daten
- Admin-Interface für Tasting Set Management

### 7. Testing Strategy

#### Model Tests
```dart
test('should create TastingSet with default values', () {
